<h1>About Tanya Angel</h1>

<p>
Tanya Angel is a music artist, visual creator, and founder of TanyAngel Production.
Her work combines music, futuristic fashion concepts, and cinematic visual storytelling.
</p>

<p>
Through experimental visuals and original music, she creates a unique artistic universe
where sound, fashion design, and digital art come together.
Many of her projects feature surreal AI fashion concepts developed specifically
for music videos and visual productions.
</p>

<p>
Alongside her artistic work, Tanya Angel operates TanyAngel Production,
a creative studio producing music videos, fashion show coverage,
artist interviews, and promotional video content.
</p>

<p>
Her creative philosophy focuses on storytelling through visuals and sound,
capturing the identity and energy of artists, fashion designers,
and live events.
</p>
